.SS Setting the force parameter
The second parameter can be used to determine whether the class is
included or not.
This example would include the `c' class only if the browser window is
over 1000 pixels wide:
.IP
.EX
span.classList.toggle(\[dq]c\[dq], window.innerWidth > 1000);
.EE
